TEST STEPS

1. Open class1 and class2 editors;
2. Press File-Restart;
3. Make sure that when eclipse is restarted class1 and class2 editors are opened;
4. Go to Preferences/General/Editors and check "Close editors automatically";
5. Press File/Restart and make sure that when eclipse is restarted - no editors are opened. 
